---
layout: base.njk
title: Контакти
description: Свържете се с мен за въпроси или за да запазите час.
---

<section class="py-4 md:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl w-full mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col gap-8">
        <div class="w-full text-left">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-blue">Контакти</h1>
            <p class="mt-3 text-primary-deepsea max-w-3xl">Имате въпроси или желаете да запазите час? Свържете се с мен.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-md">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-deepsea mb-4">Информация</h2>
                <div class="space-y-4 text-primary-dark-gray">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8">
                            <img src="{{ '/assets/images/location.png' | url }}" alt="Адрес" class="w-5 h-5 object-contain">
                        </span>
                        <p class="leading-relaxed">бул. Цариградско шосе 123, София 1000, България</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
                        <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8">
                            <img src="{{ '/assets/images/phone.png' | url }}" alt="Телефон" class="w-5 h-5 object-contain">
                        </span>
                        <p class="leading-relaxed"><a href="tel:+359888765432" class="text-primary-blue hover:underline">0888 765 432</a></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
                        <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8">
                            <img src="{{ '/assets/images/mail.png' | url }}" alt="Имейл" class="w-5 h-5 object-contain">
                        </span>
                        <p class="leading-relaxed"><a href="mailto:info@frigoexpress.bg" class="text-primary-blue hover:underline">info@frigoexpress.bg</a></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-primary-sand/30">
                        <p class="text-sm text-primary-dark-gray">Приемаме обаждания по всяко време на денонощието.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white overflow-hidden p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-md">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-deepsea mb-4">Локация</h2>
                <iframe class="rounded-2xl" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2955.6583307721944!2d24.796751600000007!3d42.2003724!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x14acd37751932f0d%3A0xaa89de8ae74b1b73!2z0YPQuy4g0KXRgNC40YHRgtC-INCR0L7RgtC10LIgNjYsIDQxMzUg0J_Qu9C-0LLQtNC40LI!5e0!3m2!1sbg!2sbg!4v1764956661479!5m2!1sbg!2sbg" width="100%" height="350" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-4 md:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl w-full mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="bg-white/80 rounded-3xl shadow-md p-8 md:p-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary-blue mb-6">Форма за контакт</h2>
            <form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" class="space-y-5" id="contact-form">
                {% if mailKey %}
                    <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="{{ mailKey | escape }}">
                {% endif %}
                <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="Ново запитване от сайта">
                <input type="hidden" name="redirect" value="{{ '/blagodarya/' | url }}">
                <input type="checkbox" name="botcheck" class="hidden" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off">
                <div class="">
                    <label for="contact-name" class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary-deepsea">Име и фамилия</label>
                    <input id="contact-name" name="name" type="text"  class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-primary-sand/70 bg-white/70 px-4 py-3 text-primary-volcanic placeholder:text-primary-dune/60 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-evergreen/50 focus:border-primary-evergreen transition" required>
                </div>
                <div class="">
                    <label for="contact-email" class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary-deepsea">Имейл</label>
                    <input id="contact-email" name="email" type="email"  class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-primary-sand/70 bg-white/70 px-4 py-3 text-primary-volcanic placeholder:text-primary-dune/60 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-evergreen/50 focus:border-primary-evergreen transition" required>
                </div>
                <div class="">
                    <label for="contact-message" class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary-deepsea">Вашето запитване</label>
                    <textarea id="contact-message" name="message" rows="5"  class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-primary-sand/70 bg-white/70 px-4 py-3 text-primary-volcanic placeholder:text-primary-dune/60 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-evergreen/50 focus:border-primary-evergreen transition resize-none" required></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="pt-2">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-primary w-full md:w-auto px-8 py-3 rounded-3xl">Изпрати</button>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-primary-dune/80" id="contact-form-result"></p>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
